{"tid":2233274,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 黃金魚強","createTime":"2020-10-07T04:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T06:29:55.000Z","uid":33359,"like":83,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"e448331721a7d497937eca4c04e261f1ea1bcacf","tid":2233274,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAF51sc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAF51sc.jpg&h=4aad9d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人提議我油塘試呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫咗個黃金魚強<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身以為係咸強黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知原來係就咁炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即叫即炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落層皮好脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為千島醬個味太濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係好食得出魚味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係個魚強既彈牙程度基本上係我食過最彈牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係當乒乓波打都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個胰臟好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a66bc3e9e6c9934fa556cb55a2ef01180a900c","tid":2233274,"uid":213913,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"第一師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dd29101e40167ae297b186ee76a81359e8fd16","tid":2233274,"uid":200253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"食咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3094c29d071