score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"究竟你有冇食菜，屙唔屙到屎？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"便秘兩日了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"等我幫你通通佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee78548ab0991033dcff4fe9752a86d64f85239","tid":2233274,"uid":258794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e448331721a7d497937eca4c04e261f1ea1bcacf","tid":2233274,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAF51sc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAF51sc.jpg&h=4aad9d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人提議我油塘試呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫咗個黃金魚強<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身以為係咸強黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知原來係就咁炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即叫即炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落層皮好脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為千島醬個味太濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係好食得出魚味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係個魚強既彈牙程度基本上係我食過最彈牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係當乒乓波打都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個胰臟好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"好食師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f343c266ea9841775f86095c0d872dbb43f76eb8","tid":2233274,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"食落個胰臟好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376696f48dce20e20c791d4eac8b1b106ed5a177","tid":2233274,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"134deae0a6afcdd5172ef85a9a46e81572123185","tid":2233274,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e60cb6bc09e039d478e1afab1a64873718f8f64","tid":2233274,"uid":302668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"鯉魚門街市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"你點知的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}